'''ITV4'''是[[英國|英國]]的一個[[免費電視頻道接收|免費電視]]頻道，開播於2005年11月1日。該頻道由[[獨立電視公司|獨立電視公司]]的子公司[[ITV數位頻道|ITV數位頻道]]所有。ITV4主要播出體育、警察題材、[[占士邦|占士邦]]電影、美國喜劇和電視劇、ITV經典劇集等類型的節目。在2020年，ITV4是英國男性觀眾第五多的數位頻道，觀眾中66%是男性<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.itvmedia.co.uk/advertising-on-itv/our-channels#channel-itv4 |title=ITV4 |publisher=ITV Media |access-date=2021-07-03 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309185927/https://www.itvmedia.co.uk/advertising-on-itv/our-channels#channel-itv4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==歷史==
外界曾認為ITV4將取代既有的{{link-en|男性和摩托|Men & Motors}}頻道，類似ITV3取代格拉納達+（Granada Plus）頻道<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/itv4-takes-men-motors-slot/464997|title=ITV4 takes Men and Motors slot|publisher=campaign|access-date=2021-07-03|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703090851/https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/itv4-takes-men-motors-slot/464997|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但後來獨立電視公司表示將在開設ITV4的同時保留男性和摩托頻道，兩個頻道一度同時在Freeview上存在。2005年11月1日，ITV4正式開始播出。除了英國之外，愛爾蘭亦可收看到ITV4的節目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theairwaves.net/index.php/cable/4396-gordon |title=UPC lose ITV's digital channels |publisher=TheAirwaves |date=2011-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906230418/http://www.theairwaves.net/index.php/cable/4396-gordon |archive-date=2011-09-06 |access-date=2021-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。ITV4亦有在盧森堡註冊，以在歐盟播出<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.alia.lu/en/television/supervisory-activities |title=Supervisory activities |publisher=ALIA |date=2021-07-01 |access-date=2021-07-03 |archive-date=2021-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627141512/https://www.alia.lu/en/television/supervisory-activities |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.alia.lu/assets/upload/files/2021-03-17Liste-des-services-de-television-maj-mars-2021_site-ALIA.pdf |title=Services de télévision sur antenne soumis au contrôle de l’ALIA |publisher=ALIA |date=2021-07-01 |access-date=2021-07-03 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320130933/https://www.alia.lu/assets/upload/files/2021-03-17Liste-des-services-de-television-maj-mars-2021_site-ALIA.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==附屬頻道==
===ITV4 +1===
2008年10月後期，ITV表示將在這一年年底開播ITV4的時移頻道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.watchallchannelslive.com/2016/07/itv4-plus-1.html|title=Itv4 +1 Live Stream|publisher=Live TV Online|date=2012-05-31|access-date=2014-06-29|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919040441/http://www.watchallchannelslive.com/2016/07/itv4-plus-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年12月1日開始，ITV4 +1開始在天空廣播上播出。
===ITV4 HD===
2010年11月15日，ITV4開始在天空廣播上播出[[高畫質電視|高畫質電視]]同步聯播頻道'''ITV4 HD'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itvplc.com/media/news/itv-2010-interim-results|title=ITV plc 2010 Interim Results & Sky deal|publisher=ITV plc|date=2010-08-03|access-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712130553/http://www.itvplc.com/media/news/itv-2010-interim-results|archive-date=2014-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Laughlin | first = Andrew | title = ITV3 HD and ITV4 HD go live on Sky | work = Tech News | publisher = Digital Spy | date = 2010-11-15 | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a287927/itv3-hd-and-itv4-hd-go-live-on-sky.html#~oID5COY1qVFmMr | access-date = 2014-06-29 | archive-date = 2014-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140810111159/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a287927/itv3-hd-and-itv4-hd-go-live-on-sky.html#~oID5COY1qVFmMr | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該頻道最初是付費頻道<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/mar/02/itv-programme-making-talent|title=ITV earmarks £12m to hire new talent to break international hit drought|publisher=The Guardian|date=2011-03-02|location=London|first=Mark|last=Sweney|access-date=2014-06-29|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628145940/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/mar/02/itv-programme-making-talent|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/aug/03/itv-unveils-pay-tv-push|title=ITV unveils pay-TV push|publisher=The Guardian|date=2010-08-03|location=London|first=Mark|last=Sweney|access-date=2014-06-29|archive-date=2021-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628145939/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/aug/03/itv-unveils-pay-tv-push|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年3月14日，ITV4開始在[[維珍媒體|維珍媒體]]上播出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://about.virginmedia.com/press-release/9306/virgin-media-introduces-hdelightful-itv-channels |title=Virgin Media introduces HDelightful ITV channels |publisher=Virgin Media |date=2013-03-14 |access-date=2013-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927150231/http://about.virginmedia.com/press-release/9306/virgin-media-introduces-hdelightful-itv-channels |archive-date=2013-09-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。ITV4 HD的高畫質節目包括電影和體育賽事<ref>{{cite web | last = Laughlin | first = Andrew | title = ITV to air British Touring Cars in HD | work = Media News | publisher = Digital Spy | date = 2010-10-11 | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a281385/itv-to-air-british-touring-cars-in-hd.html#~oID8L0oIzpxd1N | access-date = 2014-06-29 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924051527/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a281385/itv-to-air-british-touring-cars-in-hd.html#~oID8L0oIzpxd1N | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
